# Provenance: hand-authored corruption cases distilled from common real-world M3U bugs.
# Exercises: dangling EXTINF with no URL, a stray non-URL line, blank lines, an HLS tag,
#            and a bare (EXTINF-less) URL. Tolerant parsing must skip-and-count, not fail.
#EXTM3U

#EXTINF:-1,Has A URL
http://headend.example/live/ok1.ts

#EXTINF:-1,This EXTINF Has No URL Before The Next One
#EXTINF:-1,Recovered After Dangling
http://headend.example/live/ok2.ts

this is a stray line that is not a url and must be skipped

#EXT-X-VERSION:3
http://headend.example/live/bare3.ts
